    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It has significant mechanical issues that will require professional attention, and the exterior shows heavy wear, including large dents, rusted panels, and peeling clear coat. The interior is also in rough shape with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be a suitable project car for a mechanic or a source for parts, but it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
