      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From its flawless exterior finish to its factory-fresh interior, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality. Fully inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
