    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and stayed on top of every single service. You won't find a scratch on it! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
